    <lb n="29"/>ἡμῶν ἀναλώμασιν κατ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὰ</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὴν</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δύν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αμ</supplied>ιν τῆς αὐτῆς διαλυτικῆς 

